node.text:
This recipe really takes the biscuit!

BLACK FOREST GATEAUX ICE BOX CAKE
INGREDIENTS
* 	300g rectangular chocolate sandwich biscuits 
* 	4 cups tinned cherries
* 	1/2 cup water
* 	3/4 cup sugar
* 	2 tbsp cornstarch
* 	800l double cream
* 	200g cream cheese
* 	100g icing sugar
* 	200g dark chocolate
* 	200g milk chocolate
* 	300ml double cream
* 	800ml double cream
* 	50ml icing sugar
* 	Fresh cherries, to serve
* 	Chopped chocolate, to serve

 #delicious #foodgoals #nobakedessert #chocolatecake #noleftovers

node.text:
CHICKEN PARM DEEP DISH PIZZA
INGREDIENTS
* 	8 chicken breasts
* 	150g plain flour
* 	4 eggs
* 	200g breadcrumbs
* 	50g parmesan
* 	1 tsp Italian seasoning
 
* 	1 tbsp olive oil
* 	3 cloves of garlic, diced
* 	1/2 tsp chilli flakes
* 	1l tomato passata
* 	1 onion
* 	20g butter
* 	1 tsp salt
* 	1 tsp sugar
 
* 	140ml warm water
* 	1 tsp instant yeast
* 	1 tbsp granulated sugar
* 	2 tbsp olive oil
* 	1/2 tsp salt
* 	225g bread flour
 
* 	200g mozzarella, sliced
* 	750g parmesan, grated
* 	Basil, to serve

¾ cups butter, softened
¾ cup brown sugar
¼ cup granulated sugar
1 ½ cups flour
1 tsp salt
1 tsp vanilla
2 tsp milk
1 cup chocolate chips
Mousse:
200g dark chocolate, chopped fine
3/4 cup whipping cream, hot
2 1/4 cup whipping cream, cold
1 tsp vanila
2 tbsp icing sugar
2 cups heavy cream, hot
454g dark chocolate finely chopped

* 	750g parmesan, grated
* 	Basil, to serve

node.text:
This recipe is the perfect dessert for you! 

COOKIE DOUGH MOUSSE CAKE
INGREDIENTS
Cookie Dough:
¾ cups butter, softened
¾ cup brown sugar
¼ cup granulated sugar
1 ½ cups flour
1 tsp salt
1 tsp vanilla
2 tsp milk
1 cup chocolate chips
Mousse:
200g dark chocolate, chopped fine
3/4 cup whipping cream, hot
2 1/4 cup whipping cream, cold
1 tsp vanila
2 tbsp icing sugar
2 cups heavy cream, hot
454g dark chocolate finely chopped

 #delicious #foodgoals #nobakedessert #chocolatecake #noleftovers

Tom J (@teeeeeejj) here. This garlic cheese tomato pasta was so delicious and fun and easy to make. I do hope you enjoy watching it. In Italy you get told off if your pasta’s too saucy but at my house you get awarded with special prizes. Imagine whipping your scarpetta out on this. Hope you’re having a nice Summer! X

node.text:
Slide into the weekend with these Teriyaki Beef Sliders

INGREDIENTS
* 	1 tbsp groundnut oil
* 	2 lb sliced rump steak
* 	1 tsp salt
* 	1 1/2 tbsp Chinese five spice
* 	1 tbsp oil
* 	1 tbsp sesame seeds
* 	3 garlic cloves, crushed
* 	5cm ginger, finely diced
* 	1 1/2 cups beef stock
* 	3 tbsp dark soy sauce
* 	1 tbsp sesame oil
* 	2 tbsp sugar
* 	2 tbsp corn starch
* 	1 tsp water
Slaw
* 	1/4 red cabbage, finely shredded
* 	1 large carrot, finely shredded
* 	1 apple, finely shredded
* 	4 spring onions, sliced
* 	1 red chilli, sliced
* 	1 cup mayonnaise
* 	1 lime, juiced
* 	1 tsp salt
* 	1 cup chopped coriander

#recipe #foodblogger #foodblogfeed #teriyaki #weekendfood  #mealideas #cheatmeal #cheatday #noleftovers #foodporn #recipes
